00:00.188 --> 00:01.568
So here's what you missed
on <i>Glee</i>...

00:01.568 --> 00:03.185
<i>Mr. Shue's in Washington,</i>

00:03.235 --> 00:04.854
<i>so now Finn's in charge</i>
<i>of the glee club, and they have</i>

00:04.905 --> 00:06.285
<i>to win Sectionals,</i>
<i>which is just a week away.</i>

00:06.307 --> 00:08.576
<i>Blaine cheated on Kurt, and</i>
<i>he's super broken up about it,</i>

00:08.610 --> 00:09.977
<i>and Kurt's the whole reason</i>
<i>Blaine came to McKinley,</i>

00:09.995 --> 00:11.412
<i>and now he's gone</i>
<i>and Blaine's all alone.</i>

00:11.446 --> 00:13.364
<i>Jake saw Ryder and Marley kiss,</i>
<i>and even though</i>

00:13.415 --> 00:15.199
<i>she's super skinny</i>
<i>and super beautiful,</i>

00:15.250 --> 00:16.951
<i>Kitty's got Marley convinced</i>
<i>that she's gaining weight.</i>

00:16.985 --> 00:18.953
The stage always adds
at least ten pounds.

00:18.987 --> 00:20.337
<i>And that's what you missed</i>
<i>on</i> Glee.

00:24.009 --> 00:26.326
The Secret Society
of Superheroes Club

00:26.344 --> 00:27.661
is now in session.

00:27.679 --> 00:29.597
It is the purpose of this club
to fight injustice,

00:29.631 --> 00:30.998
to right
all that which is wrong,

00:31.016 --> 00:32.665
and to preserve truth,
justice and peace

00:32.683 --> 00:34.001
in the halls of McKinley High.

00:34.035 --> 00:35.669
First order of business...
roll call.

00:35.687 --> 00:36.670
Go.

00:36.688 --> 00:38.005
Asian Persuasion here.

00:38.023 --> 00:40.941
My superpower is being
the mistress of manipulation.

00:40.976 --> 00:42.175
(Ã  la George W. Bush):
Blond Chameleon here.

00:42.194 --> 00:43.677
My superpower is
I can impersonate anybody.

00:43.695 --> 00:45.679
George W. Bush, heh.

00:45.697 --> 00:46.814
Tarantula Head here.

00:46.848 --> 00:48.348
My superpower is lashing you
with my dreads.

00:48.366 --> 00:49.349
(whip cracks)

00:49.367 --> 00:51.184
Sweet 'n' Spicy, here.

00:51.203 --> 00:53.320
My superpower is money.

00:53.354 --> 00:54.655
Second order of business...

00:54.689 --> 00:56.790
inducting new members
into our ever-swelling ranks.

00:56.825 --> 00:59.359
Candidates, come forth.

00:59.377 --> 01:00.794
Excited to be here, Blaine.

01:00.829 --> 01:02.463
First of all, there are no

01:02.497 --> 01:04.798
civilian identities
in here, okay?

01:04.833 --> 01:07.501
I am Nightbird
the Nocturnal Avenger.

01:07.535 --> 01:09.036
And second of all, I really
hope you're not trying

01:09.054 --> 01:10.971
to pass yourself off
as a certain telepathic leader

01:11.006 --> 01:12.372
of a certain group
of superhuman mutants

01:12.390 --> 01:14.341
because that would be
a copyright violation.

01:14.375 --> 01:16.927
Uh, I'm Dr. Y

01:16.978 --> 01:20.213
and my superpower is wheelies?

01:20.232 --> 01:22.049
Welcome, Dr. Y.
Next.

01:22.067 --> 01:25.385
I'm Queen Bee
and I can sting like a bitch.

01:25.403 --> 01:26.386
(buzzes)

01:26.404 --> 01:28.188
Welcome, Queen Bee.
Next.

01:28.222 --> 01:29.406
I'm the Human Brain.

01:31.359 --> 01:32.326
Welcome, Human Brain.

01:32.360 --> 01:33.444
(phone chimes)

01:33.495 --> 01:34.561
What's this?

01:34.579 --> 01:36.330
A text just came through
on my NightPhone.

01:36.364 --> 01:38.165
"Have you talked to Kurt?"

01:38.199 --> 01:39.700
I already told you,

01:39.734 --> 01:41.335
Asian Persuasion,

01:41.369 --> 01:43.403
this account is only supposed
to be for emergencies,

01:43.421 --> 01:45.039
and you cannot use
your powers of manipulation

01:45.073 --> 01:46.073
to coax me into getting

01:46.091 --> 01:48.408
back with my ex, so stop trying.

01:49.577 --> 01:51.512
What is it, Chai Tea?

01:51.546 --> 01:53.013
Emergency in the choir room.

01:53.048 --> 01:54.098
To the choir room.

