02:07.445 --> 02:09.145
Someone took
your Nationals trophy

02:09.197 --> 02:11.264
and left that laptop
in its place.

02:11.283 --> 02:12.399
ARTIE:
Who leaves a laptop?

02:12.433 --> 02:14.267
Someone rich,

02:14.286 --> 02:15.936
someone who wanted
to send us a message.

02:15.954 --> 02:17.738
I got this.

02:21.293 --> 02:23.260
(distorted):
Greetings, New Directions!

02:23.295 --> 02:27.781
You have been living as national
champions on borrowed time,

02:27.799 --> 02:29.617
and that ends now.

02:31.119 --> 02:32.419
We have your trophy.

02:32.453 --> 02:33.754
Soon we'll have your title

02:33.788 --> 02:34.788
as well.

02:34.806 --> 02:37.057
The great reckoning is at hand...

02:37.092 --> 02:38.892
Sectionals.

02:38.927 --> 02:40.961
Your move.

